### ==========================================
### ARTICLE PLATFORM API TESTS
### Database already has 3 initial articles
### ==========================================

### 1. GET - List all articles (should show your 3 initial articles)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles

### 2. GET - Get single article by ID (Article 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/1

### 3. GET - Get article 2
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/2

### 4. GET - Get article 3
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/3

### 5. SEARCH - Search for "REST" (should return article 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/search?q=REST

### 6. SEARCH - Search for "Spring" (should return article 2)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/search?q=Spring

### 7. SEARCH - Search for "Hibernate" (should return article 3)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/search?q=Hibernate

### 8. CHECK TITLE - Existing title (should return false)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/check-title?title=REST%20API%20Architecture

### 9. CHECK TITLE - New title (should return true)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/check-title?title=Brand%20New%20Article

### 10. POPULAR - Get articles sorted by citation count (article 3 has most references)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/popular

### 11. POST - Create a new article (should return 201 Created)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My Custom Article",
  "abstractText": "This is my test article from HTTP client",
  "body": "This is the full content of my custom test article."
}

### 12. POST - Create article with references (Bonus feature)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Advanced REST Concepts",
  "abstractText": "Building on REST fundamentals",
  "body": "This article references previous REST articles for deeper understanding.",
  "referenceIds": [1, 2]
}

### 13. GET - Verify new article was created
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles

### 14. POST - Try duplicate title (should fail with 409 Conflict)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "REST API Architecture",
  "abstractText": "This should fail",
  "body": "Duplicate title not allowed"
}

### 15. GET - Non-existent article (should return 404 Not Found)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/999

### 16. SEARCH - Empty search (should return empty array)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/search?q=

### 17. SEARCH - Search with no matches (should return empty array)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/search?q=xyzabc123

### 18. GET - Check citation count on article 1 (should show how many reference it)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/1

### 19. GET - Check references on article 3 (should show it references articles 1 and 2)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/3

### 20. GET - Popular articles again after adding new ones
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/popular